Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 352
  - Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Act and Essence
  - 99
---
Placed in this world of misery, man should take no heed of the lesser
or greater sights of woe which present themselves to his view. They
are as the fleeting tints and hues which paint the empty vault of the
sky, and soon vanish into nothing.
